simpledc.dc:description:
Economical data on the country 'AUSTRIA' as calculated by the state-owned and state-sponsored entity 'STATISTIK AUSTRIA'.
Data comprises such values as the gross domestic product, and related figures.
Data contains one value of each parameter per year, in the extent from 1976 to 2020.
Data constitutes three files, as downloaded by the publisher from the creator's homepage.
volkswirtschaftliche_gesamtrechnung_hauptgroessen.xlsx the most recent data, up to 2020. the data 2016 to 2020 is only preliminary.
volkswirtschaftliche_gesamtrechnungen_1976-2007.pdf austria economic figures from 1976 to 2007 (final numbers).
volkswirtschaftliche_gesamtrechnungen_1995_-_2018.pdf austria economic figures from 1995 to 2018, final numbers, except 2016 to 2018 which are preliminiary numbers.
